Class FolderIconTheme

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.tools.swing.impl.icontheme.BaseIconTheme
      • org.gvsig.tools.swing.impl.icontheme.FolderIconTheme
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IconTheme

    public class FolderIconTheme
extends BaseIconTheme
    This class extends AbstractIconTheme and implements the abstract methods of this class. This methods are loadIcon and load. This methods allows load one icon or all icons in the resource.
